nd -> cartservice`:\n     - `POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart`:\n       - Normal Avg: 2342ms → Anomaly Avg: 9307ms (+3.97x)\n\n4. **Error Code Patterns:**\n   - `HTTP status code: 500` occurring prominently across `frontend`, with error propagation from `cartservice`.\n\n---\n\n### Root Cause Reasoning:\n1. **Error Source:** \n   - The latency spikes start from `cartservice` interactions with `redis` on operations like `HMSET` and `HGET`. \n   - Errors propagate outward to dependent services like `checkoutservice` and eventually to `frontend`.\n\n2. **Critical Dependency:**\n   - Redis-related operations (e.g., cart updates and queries) are essential for Cartservice functionality. Connectivity/bottlenecks between `cartservice` and `redis` seem to induce the observed delays and errors.\n\n3. **Cascading Failures:**\n   - Frontend errors (status 500) and response latency can be directly traced back to `cartservice` failures due to Redis bottlenecks.\n\n---\n\n### Hypothesis Validation Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"timeout\", \"cartservice->frontend\", \"cartservice->checkoutservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Latencies in HMSET and HGET (Redis operations) originating from Cartservice interactions caused bottlenecks. Errors propagated to dependent services.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis HMSET delay increased 17x (Normal: 1573ms → Anomalous: 26876ms); Cartservice GetCart delay increased 184x (Normal: 2495ms → Anomalous: 461986ms).\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis operations became critical bottlenecks under increased load/latency.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis HGET delay increased nearly 5x (Normal: 1553ms → Anomalous: 7746ms).\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "current_hypothesis": "Cartservice is the root cause of the issue due to repeated connectivity issues with Redis (redis-cart-0), causing cascading failures in downstream services, such as frontend."}
